    $ A test is just code.
    $ It Executes target code.
    $ Test a class, method or function.
    $ Check to see if the results are correct.
    $ Done manually before test libraries appeared

    //----- Benefits of Unit Testing -----//
    $ Quick feedback
    $ Automated regression checking
    $ Design Aid
    $ Improves confidence
    $ Documentation

